name: ETHFan Burn
public_notice:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract - which allows contract owners to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: ETH Fan Burn Token (EFB) is a token created to complete the ETH Fan Token Ecosystem. It allows EFT Ecosystem to create an Infinite-Compounding-Loop mechanism of endless $ETH rewarding and earning. Additionally, EthFan Burn multiplies the compounding effects of EthFanToken Ecosystem to deliver lifetime $ETH rewards to holders.
